{"tid":2140372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國傳出新布尼亞病毒 目前62人感染7人死亡","createTime":"2020-08-05T03:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T01:02:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c0d98988cb0cfff60be693ac250d87ccef816b","tid":2140372,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:17:38.000Z","msg":"中國又有新疫情在流行，目前江蘇、浙江、安徽都有民眾被感染，今年至少已62人染病，7人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n中國媒體報導稱，江蘇省南京市一名60多歲的婦女，發燒到40度，後來被確診染上「新布尼亞病毒」（new bunyavirus），這是蜱蟲叮咬引起的疾病，病症名稱為「發熱伴血小板減少綜合症」（SFTS）。<br />\n<br />\n江蘇省人民醫院今年已收治37位感染新布尼亞病毒的患者。浙江省今年有2例死亡。安徽省自從4月以來已有23人感染，5人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://eoeonews.com/doc_aW5TVEZSR0ovU3I5emVud01KZnY5QT09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feoeonews.com%2Fdoc_aW5TVEZSR0ovU3I5emVud01KZnY5QT09&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeahVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=4b253fce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://eoeonews.com/doc_aW5TVEZSR0ovU3I5emVud01KZnY5QT09</a>"},{"pid":"2cdc347e854d6c3e2376fe11a1950acedefe16dd","tid":2140372,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"日本朝日電視台引述中國媒體報導，中國傳出有人感染新布尼亞病毒，已知有7人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n報導說，一名住在江蘇省南京市的60多歲女性持續發燒高達40度，也出現咳嗽、身體疲倦等症狀，就醫後醫師診斷感染了新布尼亞病毒（new bunyavirus）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安徽省今年4月以後已知有23人感染，其中5人死亡。此外，浙江省有2人感染後死亡。<br />\n<br />\n專家表示，人體若感染新布尼亞病毒，會出現體內白血球減少、體內出血等症狀。<br />\n<br />\n中國で「新型ブニヤウイルス」7人死亡・・・60人が感染"},{"pid":"81dfd18fb9cf031fb4d12465f2b52a19d79c9af2","tid":2140372,"uid":65952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:18:55.000Z","msg":"肯定又是美國佬在搞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8d7fe5820776d61de36ce4d7d61bc81dd04f21","tid":2140372,"uid":288675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"因為佔中"},{"pid":"ed84d6bda8edb4d61e7f88e5802c5786fcc847aa","tid":2140372,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:21:27.000Z","msg":"水浸後蜱蟲浸唔死週圍飄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3292d03872fbc6f114f37692984f0e8d35b7169b","tid":2140372,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T20:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763b2e7c4b6db2081606cbbb83dfc8ed8c88fbba","tid":2140372,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T20:50:33.000Z","msg":"喔 lee d小事<br />\n死唔到幾多<br />\n強國有十四億人"},{"pid":"8ffd0ef239ef614180dccb5b9f11f8f718c6dcf1","tid":2140372,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"763b2e7c4b6db2081606cbbb83dfc8ed8c88fbba","tid":2140372,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T20:50:33.000Z","msg":"喔 lee d小事<br />\n死唔到幾多<br />\n強國有十四億人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T01:00:15.000Z","msg":"但最慘強國人會傳遍世界各地"},{"pid":"3b39dc0073d2e7199ccc3eb42de8dbbf3c9052ef","tid":2140372,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T01:02:48.000Z","msg":"又係美國傳入<br />\n好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}